1 immediately preceding an offer or an acceptance of an offer to pur-
2 chase or acquire.
3 Upon making an offer or accepting an offer to purchase or acquire
4 a single-family residence, a covered entity shall submit a completed
5 and notarized version of this form or a substantially similar form to
6 the seller or seller’s agent. Within three days of submitting the form
7 to the seller or seller’s agent, a covered entity shall submit a copy of
8 the completed and notarized form to the Department of Justice.
9
10 ATTENTION
11
12 The buyer of this single-family residence is a covered entity under
13 section 2 of this 2026 Act and is subject to the 90-day waiting period
14 described above. Any covered entity that violates the 90-day waiting
15 period or fails to submit this form as required by statute may be liable
16 for civil penalties.
17
18 IDENTIFYING INFORMATION OF BUYER(S) OF THIS
19 SINGLE-FAMILY RESIDENCE
20
